      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah. exactly. like, if the end result is always going to be nothingness, then why do we have to go through all this struggle? the anxiety, the effort, the constant need to keep going... it just feels like we're being forced to play a game that's already lost. it's like we're just delaying the inevitable for no reason.",
